  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "I want to change how we think about pages. When a new page is created, I think there should be tabs across the top, and the tabs across the top would be for the notes. I think there would be additional tabs that are specific to the actual AI:\n- Knowledge: these would be all of the key learnings\n- Decisions: which would list out all of the key decisions that are made\n- Smart rules: which tracks all of the smart rules associated with that page\nI think we may want to create an activity page, another tab called Activity, where there's just a log of everything to make it easier to debug and to have users have more confidence in the system.",
  "title": "Add tabbed interface with Knowledge, Decisions, Smart Rules, and Activity tabs",
